Skill Sovereignty Exchange (SSE) v1.0

“Human capability becomes portable verified value.”

Thesis

Modern economies over-index on fiat currency and under-index on latent human capability.

People possess unused productive capacity:

* knowledge
* labor
* craftsmanship
* mentorship
* childcare
* repair ability
* tutoring
* leadership
* cooking
* logistics
* transportation
* design
* emotional labor
* local knowledge

Current systems introduce friction:

* payment processors
* marketplace extraction fees
* advertising intermediaries
* platform monopolies
* credential gatekeepers
* discovery failures
* trust failures

SSE creates:

Verified Human Capability → Portable Value → Direct Exchange

AI becomes trust infrastructure.

Not labor replacement.

